cast.original_title: The Last Kingdom: Seven Kings Must Die
cast.overview: In the wake of King Edward's death, Uhtred of Bebbanburg and his comrades adventure across a fractured kingdom in the hopes of uniting England at last.
cast.title: The Last Kingdom: Seven Kings Must Die

details.biography: Ingrid García Jonsson was born in Skelleftea, Sweden and raised in Spain. She started working as an actress at a very young age but became known for the movie "Hermosa Juventud" (2014) for which she won and was nominated for several awards internationally. Since then she has been working in both major and independent productions, and successful TV-shows, building a very interesting career.
details.name: Ingrid García Jonsson
